      "sidebar": {
        "type": "info-card",
        "title": "能源预算管理",
        "content": "<p>能源消耗预算（Energy Consumption Budget）是 MEOS 的核心 KPI 看板：</p><ul><li><span style=\"color:#1677ff;font-weight:700;\">Annual Energy Overview</span> — 年度总能耗与达标率环形图</li><li><span style=\"color:#1677ff;font-weight:700;\">Daily Energy & Plan</span> — 每日实际能耗 vs 预算计划</li><li><span style=\"color:#1677ff;font-weight:700;\">四大模块导航</span> — 数据管理、资产管理、运维监控、风险管理</li></ul><p style=\"margin-top:12px;font-size:13px;color:#8c8c8c;\">导航路径：Energy & Carbon Management > Budget Settlement > Energy Consumption Budget</p>"
      },
      "subtitle": "打开能源预算看板 ... 左侧是年度能耗总览和达标率 ... 下方是每日能耗趋势图。",
